column2: select avg(num) from (select a.year, (case when b.num>=0 then b.num else a.num end) as num from (select distinct year, 0 as num from df) a left outer join (select year, count(*) as num from df where type_of_care = 'annual vision checkup' and for_whom = 'child_medical_care' group by year) b on a.year = b.year)
